name: 3169/2012 Zine By Nigel Robertson
description:
This is the first edition of 3168/2012 by: Nigel Robertson

This is one epic quick read about the tragedies of humanity, and the harsh relization that we are human. Its full of hidden symbolisms, ism-schisms, hidden messages, hidden facts about esoteric societies in which all humanity is under the control of, and much more. Get your copy today while supplies last!

About the artist: Nigel is a painter / drawer / illustrator from Fresno California currently traveling the west coast in search of beauty and adventure.
